Reporting a Bug

To help resolve issues as quickly as possible, please include:

* Device model (iPhone or iPad)
* iOS version
* Lunar Lander app version
* A brief description of the issue
* Steps to reproduce the problem (if possible)
* Screenshots or screen recordings

⸻

Frequently Asked Questions

The game won’t start.

* Restart your device.
* Verify you are using the latest version of iOS.
* Update Lunar Lander from the App Store if a newer version is available.

The controls feel difficult.

That is intentional! Lunar Lander is a physics-based game where precision and practice are rewarded. Small adjustments and careful fuel management will improve your landings.

I have an idea for a new feature.

Fantastic! Player feedback helps shape future updates. Send your suggestions to the email above.

